Sentencas: Anew type of Ni-free anode material based on Co0.5Fe0.5 + SDC (Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9) was identified and evaluated using the La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.83Mg0.17O3 (LSGM) electrolyte-supported cells.
